<title type="html"><![CDATA[Classic Shell 4.2.0 beta with Windows 10 support]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=3449&amp;p=16066#p16066"><![CDATA[
Classic Shell 4.2.0 beta is released. You can download it from here: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.mediafire.com/download/r3h2yzm4wfjjagm/ClassicShellSetup_4_2_0.exe">http://www.mediafire.com/download/r3h2y ... _4_2_0.exe</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Here's what's new:<br /><ul><li>Improved support for <strong>Windows 10</strong></li><li>New ability to apply settings from XML files from command line: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.classicshell.net/faq/#install_xml">http://www.classicshell.net/faq/#install_xml</a><!-- m --></li><li>New setting to override the system DPI resolution only for the start menu</li><li>New setting to change the user picture</li><li>Improved support for touch and high resolution displays</li><li>Multiple minor improvements and bugfixes</li></ul><br />As with all beta software, glitches are possible, and it is not recommended for installation on critical systems.<br /><br />Please report any issues in the forum.<br /><br /><br />Next release is <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=4469" class="postlink">Classic Shell 4.2.1</a><br />Previous release was <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=2518" class="postlink">Classic Shell 4.1.0</a><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2">Ivo</a> — Sat Dec 13, 2014 12:03 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
